description: With his passion for cooking and throwing unforgettable parties, Chef Ricky Coghlan has certainly mastered the art of catering LA with wonderfully fresh and flavorful food, all while providing caring and attentive service. Prepare all five senses to be truly delighted by his beautifully delicious selection of Grilled Portobello Burgers, Fish & Chips, authentic Argentine Empanadas, Pan Seared Seafood,  and much more. Be sure to call on the ever-colorful Rushed Art Food Truck to cater your next event, and you’re guaranteed a tasty success.
name: Rushed Art Food Truck
